# /Generate Cursor Rules Workflow

When the user types "/Generate Cursor Rules", execute the complete deployment workflow automatically:

## 1) Git Push (Otomatik)
```bash
git add .
git commit -m "Auto-commit: $(date +%Y-%m-%d_%H:%M:%S) - Generated Cursor Rules"
git push origin main
```

## 2) Frontend Build & Deploy (Netlify)
```bash
npm run build
netlify deploy --prod --dir=dist
```

## 3) Backend Build (Railway - manuel değil, sadece build)
```bash
cd server && npm run build
```

## 4) Railway Deploy (manuel gerektiğinde)
```bash
cd server
railway login
railway link
railway up
```

## 5) Post-Deploy Tests
```bash
curl -H "x-api-key: public-demo-key" https://appsamurai-dashboard-backend-production-83b0.up.railway.app/api/health
curl -H "x-api-key: public-demo-key" https://appsamurai-dashboard-backend-production-83b0.up.railway.app/api/files
```

## Critical Rules
- Single push, ardından Netlify prod deploy
- Hata olursa kullanıcıya raporla
- Frontend URL: https://ubiquitous-sherbet-b4f6bf.netlify.app/
- Backend URL: https://appsamurai-dashboard-backend-production-83b0.up.railway.app/

